msgstr ""
"Jeżeli poziom spadnie poniżej tej wartości, wysyłanie wiadomości e-mail "
"zostanie aktywowane."

#: plugins/current_loop_tanks_monitor/templates/current_loop_tanks_monitor_setup.html:303
#: plugins/current_loop_tanks_monitor/templates/current_loop_tanks_monitor_setup.html:317
#: plugins/current_loop_tanks_monitor/templates/current_loop_tanks_monitor_setup.html:331
#: plugins/current_loop_tanks_monitor/templates/current_loop_tanks_monitor_setup.html:345
msgid ""
"As long as the level does not rise above this level, it will not allow sending "
"an email when the level drops to the minimum. This is used to block the "
