msgstr "Astral na Githubie"

#: plugins/sunrise_and_sunset/templates/sunrise_and_sunset_setup.html:3
#: plugins/sunrise_and_sunset/templates/sunrise_and_sunset_setup.html:76
msgid "Astro Sunrise and Sunset - settings"
msgstr "Astro Wschód i Zachód Słońca - ustawienia"

#: plugins/sunrise_and_sunset/templates/sunrise_and_sunset_setup.html:78
msgid ""
"The selected program that we want to run with this extension does not have to "
"be enabled in the programs, but it must have set days when we want the program "
"to run."
msgstr ""
"Wybrany program, który chcemy uruchomić z tym rozszerzeniem, nie musi być "
"włączony w programach, ale musi mieć ustawione dni, w których chcemy, aby "
"program działał."

#: plugins/sunrise_and_sunset/templates/sunrise_and_sunset_setup.html:79
msgid ""
"If the program does not have a days marked, it will not start (neither by the "
"\"run now\" button in the programs, nor by this plug-in)!"
