"Unlike the \"voice notification\" package, this extension has no connection to "
"the station scheduler (ie how the programs and the stations assigned in them "
"are set up). In this extension, the song will be played whenever the station "
"status changes, regardless of what event the status triggered (for example, "
"manual mode, scheduler, or some other plugin...)"
